{"tid":2189757,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來「保就業計劃津貼」要與全民驗武肺掛勾，政府授權「壹台電梯有限公司」不發放薪金給不提交驗武肺證明之員工","createTime":"2020-09-05T06:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T07:04:19.000Z","uid":230104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"275d5258bcead1b6accadab8795e431b100e1eba","tid":2189757,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:14:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200904/EL3NEXAR35FPJPL5ETRNWPQEPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200904%2FEL3NEXAR35FPJPL5ETRNWPQEPY%2F&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs41Scv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=b14d420d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200904%2FEL3NEXAR35FPJPL5ETRNWPQEPY%2F&h=859dd03d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200904/EL3NEXAR35FPJPL5ETRNWPQEPY/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Zq1L64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Zq1L64.png&h=4260d648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本港武漢肺炎疫情稍見緩和，不少公司回復正常上班，昨天（3日）4名經全民檢測發現陽性的舊個案中，其中一人是被公司要求有陰性報告才前往檢測。《蘋果》獲悉，有電梯公司要求員工交出核酸檢測樣本，否則不會獲派1萬元補貼<span class=\"red\">；公司高層亦直認不交樣本「有違政府抗疫原則」，有權不派發津貼給相關員工。</span>本報就事件向相關政府部門查詢，創新辦稱不會就個別個案作出評論，<span class=\"red\">勞工處則只籲僱主與僱員雙方應透過溝通磋商，協商有關安排。</span>"},{"pid":"26624d7c56d995de811844deaaf36f5d36ff0079","tid":2189757,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:15:54.000Z","msg":"到底係保就業津貼，還是保僱主荷包？ 仲有特權大支野用來要脅員工？仲自稱「有權」？"},{"pid":"5e4267b0918000fc8369cfa312801ede5b2d1b6d","tid":2189757,"uid":174120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"26624d7c56d995de811844deaaf36f5d36ff0079","tid":2189757,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:15:54.000Z","msg":"到底係保就業津貼，還是保僱主荷包？ 仲有特權大支野用來要脅員工？仲自稱「有權」？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:16:28.000Z","msg":"保僱主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/